### AI Codebase Intelligence — API Test File
### Install "REST Client" extension in VS Code, then click "Send Request"

@base = http://localhost:8000

# ─────────────────────────────────────────
### 1. Health Check
GET {{base}}/health

###

### 2. Root
GET {{base}}/

###

### 3. Ingest a Repository
POST {{base}}/api/ingest-repo
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "repo_url": "https://github.com/pallets/flask",
  "force": false
}

###

### 4. Check Repo Status  (replace repo_id with what step 3 returned)
GET {{base}}/api/repo-status/pallets__flask

###

### 5. Ask a Question
POST {{base}}/api/ask-question
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "repo_id": "pallets__flask",
  "question": "How does routing work in Flask?"
}

###

### 6. Trace Execution Flow
POST {{base}}/api/trace-flow
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "repo_id": "pallets__flask",
  "entry_function": "full_dispatch_request",
  "max_depth": 5
}

###

### 7. Architecture Overview
GET {{base}}/api/get-architecture/pallets__flask

###

### 8. List All Functions
GET {{base}}/api/list-functions/pallets__flask?limit=30

###

### 9. Reload Session (after server restart)
POST {{base}}/api/reload-session/pallets__flask
